Package: miRDriver
Type: Package
Title: miRDriver: A Tool to Infer Copy Number Derived miRNA-Gene Networks in Cancer
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person("Banabithi", "Bose", email="banabithi.bose@marquette.edu", role=c("aut")), person("Serdar", "Bozdag", email="serdar.bozdag@marquette.edu", role="aut"),
           person("Matthew", "Moravec", email="matt.moravec222@gmail.com", role = "cre"))
Description: Four step package to find regulation micro RNA. The intermediate steps include finding gistic
             regions, finding differentilly expressed genes, gathering cis genes for trans genes and selecting
             potential micro RNA regulators. These steps are designed to be part of the pipeline, but can be used
             individually if it fits ones needs.
